Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.83,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Gouda Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:15.61,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I'm \Na first-year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.17,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after I entered high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:26.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with Yamato after \Nsaving her from a groper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.00,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Get off this train at the next station!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.16,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.19,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:36.72,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.22,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.97,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,But Yamato had fallen for Suna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.73,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:44.60,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:50.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna seems to have a thing for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:14.05,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, \Nyou're always helping me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:20.93,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:32.10,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, could it be without Sunakawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.94,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'd like it to be just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:40.18,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's finally ready to ask for \Nadvice with her relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.49,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:23.55,Title1,Sign 0320,0000,0000,0000,,My Blue Ogre
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, was I late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're still five minutes early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.52,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, is it just my imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.08,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,or does she look extra-ridiculously cute today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:02.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I thought it shouldn't always be cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I made cake salé today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Cake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You might take a bite, thinking it's \Nsweet, but it's actually salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So don't take a bite, thinking it's sweet, \Nbecause it's actually salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.28,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She said it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:27.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:30.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've never tasted anything like it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:38.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You always eat a lot of my baking. \NThat makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I brought tea today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, Sunakawa-kun bought drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and that was really considerate of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:03.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Suna is really considerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a girlfriend, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And he spoke highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't cheat on a girl, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:14.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's smart and good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:21.42,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do much about how people feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:26.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Take it from someone who's known him \Nsince we were three years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You have my guarantee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's a good guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:34.89,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... I'm a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:39.15,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make you uncomfortable \Nby confessing my feelings to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.69,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.53,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,They'd make a great couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.03,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She thanked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.79,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She lifted the beam with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.96,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes, \NI get to eat tasty cake like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.02,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:03.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I'm the Red Ogre.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.13,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't be like the Blue Ogre, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:10.54,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I do want the people I care for to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:13.33,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, Suna's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:26.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Something got into my eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, I guess my contacts shifted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.71,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.86,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why was she crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:56.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something to Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:57.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"Nothing"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you aren't even going \Nto say, "I'm coming in"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did Yamato cry when \NI told her about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:07.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She cried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she likes you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you're the idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Yamato-san likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me! She likes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you're cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You're cool, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.20,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san said you were cool, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting really tiresome. \NCan I just tell you everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:08.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When we met Yamato-san in the \Npark to return her phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,you vanished into the restroom \Nat some point, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:15.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, she'd told me a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.34,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.63,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.56,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A girlfriend, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.75,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.29,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:29.86,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.74,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.82,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.16,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.41,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the type who \Ncould hide that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:43.08,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.29,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help myself, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:50.05,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He was so cool yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:54.44,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but fall for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Fall for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But that time in my room, \Nshe didn't want you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:05.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.61,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.23,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.90,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:14.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Her face totally said she wanted \Nto spend more time with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She probably didn't want me to go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:19.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,because she'd be too nervous \Nif she were alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's always looking at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:25.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're always staring at her. \NOf course she can't look you in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Think back harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for you to develop \Na better eye for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:37.30,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.31,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No way. It can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:44.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You said Yamato's a nice girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She is a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:49.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with her, she only talks \Nabout how she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Till now, you've had poor taste in girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:10:00.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,All the girls you liked talked smack \Nabout you behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.47,Default - flashback,Yuzuha,0000,0000,0000,,I think Gouda likes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.82,Default - flashback,Mao,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.27,Default - flashback,Misaki,0000,0000,0000,,His face is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.86,Default - flashback,Kayomi,0000,0000,0000,,Way too huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.47,Default - flashback,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,He's loud and annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.16,Default - flashback,Class,0000,0000,0000,,But he's always looking at you, Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.36,Default - flashback,Sato,0000,0000,0000,,That's seriously creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You should seriously have better taste in girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd want to date girls that talk \Nsmack about your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,You always turned them down when they \Ntold you how they felt about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you're the manliest of men!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I said you didn't have a pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely have a pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:48.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't believe that Yamato likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:53.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you might find it hard unless \Nyou hear her say it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.82,Default,SMom,0000,0000,0000,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.63,Default,SMom,0000,0000,0000,,Someone named Yamato-san's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.64,Default,SMom,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:20.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:31.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I came without any notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I cried in front of Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How can I explain it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun looked really uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:59.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun's always suggesting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's always talking about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was turning me down \Nin a roundabout way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and that just got tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:08.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:09.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll meet \Nanyone else like Takeo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you may be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:34.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:38.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I like Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Say it one last time, so the point gets across.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really like Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be sure, say it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I like Takeo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:51.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you tell her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You manipulated me, Sunakawa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:22.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't get it through his thick \Nskull without hearing for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked you from the day we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked you from the day we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.91,SignA,Sign 1414,0000,0000,0000,,We Are Happy \N\NThank You, \N\NSunakawa-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:15.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sign of her gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:22.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sunakawa-kun, thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:28.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I have a friend who's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have her pic here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to try to spread the love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.85,SFX-RedBlack,Sign 1431,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(93,1)}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.35,SFX-BlueWhite - Copy,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,1)}I see
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,don't be so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I like seeing you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.91,SignB,Sign 1453,0000,0000,0000,,This cake looks like it \Nhas a fairy or something \Nhiding inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:58.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, you really are like the Blue Ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the kindergarten play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You were the Blue Ogre, \Nand I was the Red Ogre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,All the moms cried a river, watching you \Nact out the two ogres' friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:10.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:14.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's the story about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:20.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:26.19,Play,Sign 1520,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Ogre {\c&H917B57&}Who Cried
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:23.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,a kind-hearted Red Ogre lived all by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Ogre wanted to \Nmake friends with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:35.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but they were afraid of the ogre \Nand kept their distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:42.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It made the Red Ogre sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But his friend, the Blue Ogre, tells him
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,that the Blue Ogre will go stir \Nthings up in the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and the Red Ogre should come beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:52.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Ogre thought that'd change the \Npeople's opinion about the Red Ogre,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and make them willing to be friends with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Ogre went to the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.73,0:16:00.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and went on a rampage, although he \Nwas careful not to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Ogre pretended to beat the Blue Ogre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Ogre pretended \Nto be defeated and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.81,0:16:19.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Henceforth, the villagers \Ntrusted the Red Ogre
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.87,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and would come over to his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:26.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he had human friends, \Nthe Red Ogre led a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:37.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he became worried about the \NBlue Ogre, who'd stopped coming by,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.25,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,and he went to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:55.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Red Ogre crossed entire mountains and \Nvalleys to reach the Blue Ogre's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:05.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,he found that the Blue \NOgre had left on a journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,leaving behind a letter to the Red Ogre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The letter said,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:11.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"You finally became friends with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you're friendly to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:17.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,they'll just come to mistrust you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:22.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Ogre had left the Red \NOgre without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:32.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Ogre's such a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:36.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:39.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could go that far, \Neven for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Ogre's way too nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's got way too much integrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:43.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:44.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.33,Default,TY,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, they were friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who wouldn't want their friends to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's just normal, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.91,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:22.37,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna might have always been \Nkeeping an eye out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo... can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.58,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.36,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice. It's a bromance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bromance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.69,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I got asked a lot why we're even friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:10.29,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess it wasn't only because \Nwe were neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This one's another winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:51.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What kind is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're madelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, madelines?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.00,SignC,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, Age 5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.44,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.46,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.70,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.42,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.88,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Transfo—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.93,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see my mad skills just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:32.59,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.85,SFX-BlackWhite,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\fad(606,1)}I wouldn't call those mad skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.85,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Orya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.02,SignC,Sign 2138,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, Age 10
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.79,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.98,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always fall into this hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.62,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because you aren't jumping over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:55.41,Default,SSis,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Takeo's always up close and personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:57.83,SignD,Sign 2152,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(361,1)}Sunakawa Ai \N\N(Junior High School Student)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.23,SignF,Sign 2200,0000,0000,0000,,Talk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.23,SignE,Sign 2200,0000,0000,0000,,Volume \N\N\N\NBrightness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.80,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.14,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.41,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,What, did something funny happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.35,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom break!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:23.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, Takeo-kun's so up close and \Npersonal, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:28.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It makes my heart skip a beat, you know?
